  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>The <b><a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd\" title=\"Shepherd\">Shepherd</a></b> was a prophet during the Dance of the Dragons. It can also refer to: \n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Characters\">Characters</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shepherd_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Characters\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Shepherd\" title=\"House Shepherd\">House Shepherd</a>, an ironborn family.\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Daegon_Shepherd\" title=\"Daegon Shepherd\">Daegon Shepherd</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Qarl_Shepherd\" title=\"Qarl Shepherd\">Qarl Shepherd</a></li></ul></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ralf_the_Shepherd\" title=\"Ralf the Shepherd\">Ralf the Shepherd</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/False_Shepherd\" title=\"False Shepherd\">False Shepherd</a></li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Shepherd\" title=\"Great Shepherd\">Great Shepherd</a>, a deity worshipped in Lhazar.</li>\n<li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd_reborn\" title=\"Shepherd reborn\">Shepherd reborn</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Streets\">Streets</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Shepherd_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Streets\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Shepherd%27s_Way\" title=\"Shepherd&#39;s Way\">Shepherd's Way</a></li></ul>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Titles\">Titles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><